### LESSON 253: SMOKE TEST — UPDATE AN EXISTING TODO
# PATCH communicates a partial update. Replace the id with one that currently
# exists in the store; the server responds with the updated entity.
#
# Content-Type is required so `express.json()` parses the body into `req.body`
# (otherwise `req.body.text` would come through as undefined).
PATCH http://localhost:3000/todos/0.123456789
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Updated text"
}
